  "detailed_description": "In <strong>Danplace</strong>, you are trapped in an unknown and dangerous place, to escape you need to lower bridges and fight to survive the dangers of this terrible place.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dangers:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Giant</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733190/extras/1b24514588180eb7c84c1d102a5e849f.avif?t=1703082794\" width=616 height=353 /></span><br><strong>This enemy is big and strong, beware of him!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Human</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733190/extras/30210c524b029356096655a3b8bf6f3b.avif?t=1703082794\" width=616 height=353 /></span><br><strong>This is a human, he is the weakest enemy, but he has a sharp axe.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Spider</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1733190/extras/4addb28ae65365c4293617462315c6aa.avif?t=1703082794\" width=616 height=353 /></span><br><strong>The spider is the strongest and most resistant enemy, be careful when facing it!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHARACTERISTICS:</strong></h2>- 3D Hand painted graphics<br><br>- Simple combat<br>- Short duration (20 to 40 minutes)",
